---
title: Lemony Chicken Paillard with Roasted Sweet Potato Wedges and Gremolata
description: Gremolata is a chopped herb condiment traditionally made with lemon zest, garlic and parsley. This zesty dressing is delicious on pan-fried chicken, with cumin-roasted sweet potatoes on the side!
